folder: Greenwich Street & Warren Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
Greenwich Street, south from Warren Street as photo-
graphed from the Ninth Avenue Elevated Line station there.
At the left is the massive white structure that is the
newely erected U. S. Office Building and Post Office.

June 1940

P. L. Sperr
